headline: Otis Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Advisory
summary: Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) will host a conference call on Wednesday, January 29, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. ET. Otis Chair, CEO & President Judy Marks and Executive Vice President & CFO Cristina Mendez will discuss the company's full year and fourth quarter results and 2025 outlook.
